Invento — Smart Inventory & Expiry Management
│
├── ⚙️ Configuration & Deployment
│   ├── .git/                # Git source control tracking
│   ├── .gitignore           # Tells Git which files to ignore (like .vercel)
│   └── .vercel/             # Vercel deployment configuration
│
├── 📂 Static Assets
│   └── assets/              # Folder for images, SVGs, or external fonts
│
├── 🎨 Styling (CSS)
│   ├── shared.css           # Global modern flat dark theme & component library
│   ├── styles.css           # Base design tokens and typography
│   ├── admin.css            # Styles for the Admin panel
│   └── suggestions.css      # Styles for the AI Insights page
│
├── 🧠 Logic & Data (JavaScript)
│   ├── auth.js              # User authentication, registration, and system emails
│   ├── shared.js            # Core App Engine v3 (Multi-shop, Global State, Notifs)
│   ├── script.js            # Dashboard logic (legacy bridge)
│   ├── admin.js             # System-wide analytics and user management
│   └── suggestions.js       # AI-driven inventory analysis logic
│
└── 📄 Views (HTML Pages)
    ├── index.html           # Public Landing Page
    ├── signup.html          # User Registration
    ├── login.html           # User Login
    ├── shop-select.html     # Multi-shop Switcher & Setup
    ├── dashboard.html       # Metrics & Performance Overview
    ├── products.html        # Inventory Management (Excel Import/Export)
    ├── categories.html      # Product Organization
    ├── sales.html           # Point of Sale & Transaction History
    ├── suppliers.html       # Vendor Directory
    ├── alerts.html          # Smart Stock & Expiry Monitoring
    ├── reports.html         # Business Intelligence (ABC Analysis, Profitability)
    ├── calendar.html        # Visual Expiry Timeline
    ├── expired.html         # Waste Tracking & Loss Recovery
    ├── team.html            # Role-based Access Control (RBAC)
    ├── settings.html        # Personalization & System Config
    ├── suggestions.html     # AI Insights & Optimization
    └── admin.html           # Super-admin Control Center

Modernization v3.0:
- Flat Dark Mode aesthetic with Slate/Blue palette.
- Responsive, glassmorphic UI components.
- Integrated AI Insights and multi-shop support.
- Performance-optimized data layer via localStorage.
